					<p class="font-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">Animez vos réunions et négociez avec des partenaires internationaux sans chercher vos mots.</p>
				</div>

				<div x-data="{ shown: false }" x-intersect.once="shown = true" :class="shown ? 'opacity-100 translate-y-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-y-16'" class="group bg-primary border border-primary-light p-10 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out relative cursor-pointer delay-300 md:-mt-4">
					<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-accent scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-light rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-accent transition-colors duration-500">
						<span class="text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">🎤</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-surface font-bold mb-4">Prise de Parole & Éloquence</h3>
					<p class="font-sans text-surface/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">Apprenez à maîtriser votre voix, votre intonation et votre posture en anglais face à un public.</p>
				</div>

				<div x-data="{ shown: false }" x-intersect.once="shown = true" :class="shown ? 'opacity-100 translate-y-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-y-16'" class="group bg-white border border-primary/5 p-10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-out relative cursor-pointer delay-500">
					<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-secondary scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-surface rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors duration-500">
						<span class="text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">🧭</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary font-bold mb-4">Executive Mentoring</h3>
					<p class="font-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">Un accompagnement sur-mesure (1-to-1) pour les cadres, basé sur vos situations réelles.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

